---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="页面未找到 · AI User Roadmap"
  description="这个页面暂时不存在。返回 AI User Roadmap，继续探索从入门到进阶的 AI 学习路径。"
  canonical="https://ai.heheer.com/404"
  robots="noindex, follow"
>
  <main class="not-found-page" aria-labelledby="not-found-title">
    <div class="not-found-card">
      <p class="not-found-eyebrow">404</p>
      <h1 id="not-found-title">这条路线暂时还没铺好</h1>
      <p>你访问的页面不存在，可能是链接写错了，或者这块内容还在整理中。</p>
      <a href="/" class="not-found-link">返回 Roadmap</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
